<para style="q1">

<verse number="7" style="v" />You are my hiding place; you will guard me from trouble.</para>

<para style="q1">You will surround me with the songs of victory.

<char style="qs">Selah</char></para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="8" style="v" />I will instruct you and teach you in the way which you should go.</para>

<para style="q1">I will instruct you with my eye upon you.</para>
